# Breathe Cities — breathe-cities-design-hub environment template
# Copy to .env.local and fill in real values. .env.local is gitignored — never commit secrets.

# Mapbox GL JS access token. Public (browser-exposed) by design — scope/restrict it in the
# Mapbox dashboard for the breath-cities-design-hub.netlify.app domain. Required by the AQ
# Network concept (NetworkGlobe + SensorGrowthMap) and by the Best Practice Roadmap city
# detail pages (CityMapHero) and the Toolkit Real-time Monitoring component.
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_TOKEN=

# OpenAQ v3 API key. SERVER-SIDE ONLY — never browser-exposed (no NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix).
# Read by /api/stations and /api/locations route handlers via src/lib/openaq/client.ts.
# Powers the city detail Mapbox embed (best-practice-roadmap-v2/city/[slug]) and the
# Real-time Monitoring toolkit component. Live live-source fetches fall back to committed
# snapshots when the key is absent or the upstream is unreachable; configuring the key
# enables the explicit `?source=live` path and the on-demand recapture flow.
OPENAQ_API_KEY=
